description: Describes the current Infrastructure Performance metric subscriptions.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: One or more filters. (dict) --- A filter name and value pair that is used to return a more specific list of results from a describe operation. Filters can be used to match a set of resources by specific criteria, such as tags, attributes, or IDs. If you specify multiple filters, the filters are joined with an AND, and the request returns only results that match all of the specified filters. For more information, see List and filter using the CLI and API in the Amazon EC2 User Guide. Name (string) --- The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive. Values (list) --- The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values. (string) ---

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive.

nested_params.name: Values
nested_params.description: The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use to retrieve the next page of results. This value is null when there are no more results to return.

nested_items.name: Subscriptions
nested_items.description: Describes the current Infrastructure Performance subscriptions.

nested_items.name: Source
nested_items.description: The Region or Availability Zone that's the source for the subscription. For example, us-east-1.

nested_items.name: Destination
nested_items.description: The Region or Availability Zone that's the target for the subscription. For example, eu-west-1.

nested_items.name: Metric
nested_items.description: The metric used for the subscription.

nested_items.name: Statistic
nested_items.description: The statistic used for the subscription.

nested_items.name: Period
nested_items.description: The data aggregation time for the subscription.
